  "libraryVersion": "2025.06",
  "lastValidated": "2026-06-27",
  "pluginNotes": "Text is a native renderer \u2014 there is no SAP Figma instance for sap.m.Text. The plugin creates a figma.createText() node with: t.fontName = { family: '72', style: 'Regular' }; t.fontSize = 14; and fill bound to sapList_TextColor (default) or sapContent_LabelColor (subtle). Currently missing a buildTree handler \u2014 specs that emit Text fall through to buildSapNode and return null silently. This is a known gap fixed in the audit pass: handler added at comp === 'Text'. Status: AI specs MAY emit { component: 'Text', label: '...', props: { wrap?: bool, subtle?: bool } } anywhere body text is needed.",
